						<div class="postbody">But in this case Nintendulator is correct, sprites are delayed 1 scanline.  If you put it at 0,0 then displaying at 0,1 is right. 
<br />
<br />If your sprite is at 0,0 and you move it left, it will now be at 255,0 and should display on the right side.  If you move it up it will be at 0,255 which is off the viewing area at the bottom.</div>

